From: ARC Studio <arc-studio@local>
Date: Thu, 4 Jun 2026 18:41:50 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] feat(context): provider-aware token counter (P0-3)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Add context/token_counter.py:
  - estimate_tokens(content, provider=) public API
  - anthropic → TiktokenApproximateEstimator fallback (SDK count_tokens
    not called per-keystroke — reserved for batch pre-flight)
  - openai → tiktoken cl100k_base if installed, else heuristic
  - all other → len/4*1.33 heuristic
  - LRU-cached on (md5(content[:512]), provider)

Wire into DataStore.add_entry(): total_tokens increments on every entry.
estimate_tokens() import is lazy + try/except so TUI never crashes on
missing deps.

10 tests pass.
